thread.title: Say Goodbye to Garages as Developers Imagine a Driverless Future

author: Peter Grant
title: Say Goodbye to Garages as Developers Imagine a Driverless Future
text:
Mass adoption of driverless cars is still years away, but architects, developers and planners already are designing new projects with autonomous vehicles in mind.
